@page "/scoped-vs-singleton"
@rendermode InteractiveServer
@inject ICounterService CounterService
@inject IGlobalStateService GlobalState

<PageTitle>Scoped vs Singleton Demo</PageTitle>
<h2>Scoped vs Singleton 수명 차이</h2>

<p><strong>Scoped (CounterService):</strong> 페이지 새로고침 시마다 새 인스턴스 → 카운트 초기화</p>
<p><strong>Singleton (GlobalStateService):</strong> 앱 전체에서 같은 인스턴스 → 카운트 유지</p>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="alert alert-warning">
            <strong>Scoped 서비스</strong>
            <br />
            <p>카운트: <strong>@CounterService.GetCount()</strong></p>
            <p><small>인스턴스 ID: @CounterService.InstanceId</small></p>
            <button class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" @onclick="() => CounterService.Increment()">증가</button>
            <button class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary" @onclick="() => CounterService.Reset()">초기화</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="alert alert-success">
            <strong>Singleton 서비스</strong>
            <br />
            <p>카운트: <strong>@GlobalState.GlobalCounter</strong></p>
            <button class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" @onclick="() => GlobalState.IncrementGlobal()">증가</button>
            <p><small>메시지: @GlobalState.Message</small></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="alert alert-info mt-3">
    <strong>팁:</strong> 페이지를 새로고침하면 Scoped 카운트는 0으로 리셋되지만 Singleton 카운트는 유지됩니다.
</div>
